Cell["\<\
Suppose that the input matrix has few non-zero elements as it happens very \
often. In this case, the whole Choi matrix is not necessary to get the \
twirling of such input matrices, and it will be efficient to assume that the \
irrelevant elements of the Choi matrix vanish.\
\>", "ExampleText",
 CellID->648927842,ExpressionUUID->"cc8440ec-0691-4dc2-bc47-27413d47dce4"],

